description.en: The Killbox Game is an action-packed, somewhat bloody first-person shooter game in which players assemble elite squads and it has incorporated a tradable NFT weapon system and “play to earn” elements to make it a dynamic game. The Killbox team commits to create the first on-chain FPS game, which is accessible to EVERYONE.
